ONLINE MODE (Internet Available)
Get Weather API Data
      ↓
Receive BME280 Data via LoRa
      ↓
Receive Rain Sensor Status via LoRa
Decision Logic
Condition 1: Good Drying Conditions
Rain Probability < 70%
AND Humidity < 85%
AND Pressure Stable
AND Rain Sensor = FALSE

Action:

TFT: "Optimal drying conditions"
Siren: OFF
LED: OFF
SMS: None
Condition 2: Early Warning
Rain Probability ≥ 70%
OR
(Humidity ≥ 85%
AND Pressure Decreasing)
AND Rain Sensor = FALSE

Action:

TFT: "High possibility of rain. Prepare crops."
Send SMS warning
Siren: OFF (or short beep)
LED: Blink slowly
Condition 3: Emergency
Rain Sensor = TRUE

Action:

TFT: "RAIN DETECTED!"
Siren: ON
LED: ON
Send emergency SMS
OFFLINE MODE (No Internet)
Weather API unavailable
      ↓
Receive BME280 Data via LoRa
      ↓
Receive Rain Sensor Status via LoRa
Decision Logic
Condition 1: Good Drying Conditions
Humidity < 85%
AND Pressure Stable
AND Rain Sensor = FALSE

Action:

TFT: "Optimal drying conditions"
Siren: OFF
LED: OFF
Condition 2: Advisory Warning
Humidity ≥ 85%
AND Pressure Decreasing
AND Rain Sensor = FALSE

Action:

TFT: "Weather becoming unfavorable"
Send advisory SMS
Siren: OFF
LED: Blink slowly
Condition 3: Emergency
Rain Sensor = TRUE

Action:

TFT: "RAIN DETECTED!"
Siren: ON
LED: ON
Send emergency SMS
Complete System Flow
