Why this logic is appropriate for CroProTech
Weather API provides advance prediction.
BME280 monitors the actual drying environment and local weather trends.
Rain Sensor provides definitive confirmation that rain has started.
Automatic mode switching ensures the system continues functioning even without internet connectivity.
